name: NEW KRYPTO KICKS - Series 01, #11 - "Odd Flower" by Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool)
description: [Liner pen on notebook page with digital embellishments and color.] Hey! I'm finally getting back to my "New Krypto Kicks" faux-trading card series! Wooo! This is #11, so there will be 2 more designs in this series, and THAT'S IT! DONE! (Maybe I'll do a different series afterwards...or maybe not. We'll see...) This design was something I drew in a notebook, photographed, and then tweaked and colored with a free app on my phone. It's bright and weird and cartoony, and I'm cool with all of that. Maybe you will be too? ---Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool)
